
Complex puzzle examples:
  The maffia boss room
  Room has an antique desk, a painting, a suit case, 2 book shelfs, a ventilation opening and an exit.

  The exit lock type is CODE_ONLY_LETTER
  Behind a painting there is a wall safe, which lock is KEY type
  The antique desk has a locked drawer which lock is PASSWORD type
  Suit case has a lock which type is CODE_ONLY_NUMBER
  Chest has a KEY type lock

  First Puzzle is the Suit case. To get the code, need to search the book shelfs.
    On the first book shelf a few hidden love letters can be found.
    Each  is a word puzzle, containing 10-15 sentences, with hidden number references which is part of the password.
    First the player has to find outh which word or number can be part of the password.
    The second book shelf contains a small key for the chest.
    Opening the chest we find another love letter, which is the last part of the puzzle.
      It is either tells us that any of the previous letters was a mistake (referencing to the number) so this letter is the current version
        or it is the last part of the password
    Some letter has to be hard to figure out the passowrd, soma has to be easy.
  
  Second Puzzle is the antique desk. To get the code we have to search the opened suitcase
    There is 4-6 business documents and private letters of the maffia.
    Also a screw driver can be found within the suitcase.
    This puzzle is similar to the previous puzzle, so the player has to figure out the final password wich opens the locked desk.
    Each letter and document contains 10-15 sentences.
    Using the screwdriver we can open the ventilation opening wich contains the final document, 
      it is either tells us that any of the previous letters was a mistake (referencing to the number) so this letter is the current version
      or it is the last part of the password
  
  Third Puzzle is the safe behind the painting. To get the code, need to search the opened antique desk.
    The antique desk contains the key for the safe behind the painting
  
  The Forth final puzzle is the exit. To get the code we need to searh the opened safe.
    Within the safe we can found the maffia bos personal notbook. It contains 25-40 sencentes.
    It is the final puzzel wich is also a word puzzle. Reading the note we can get the story of the Don, and we can figure out the code, wich is the name of the Don's daughter.